member.example:
class Form
{
  [Query("-", "dontlog")]
  public string password { get; }
}

这将导致编码形式中有一个名为 dontlog-password 的字段。

interface IServerApi
{
  [Get("/expenses")]
  Task addExpense([Query(Format="0.00")] double expense);
}

调用 serverApi.addExpense(5) 将生成 URI {baseUri}/expenses?expense=5.00。
